articles.title: Turkish cave rescue underway: International teams prep to pull American from Morca sinkhole - USA TODAY
articles.description: Experienced cave diver Mark Dickey became stuck in the cave on Aug. 31 after falling ill with gastrointestinal issues.
articles.content:
International efforts to rescue an experienced caver are underway as teams deploy into the 3,000-foot deep cave to rescue a New York man.
